<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('partials/nav.ejs') -%>
        <main>
            <h1 class="visually-hidden">About Us</h1>

            <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
                <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="/images/About.png" alt="About World Eye Studio" width="mx-auto" height="400px">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-body-emphasis">About GOOD HOMES</h1>
                <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Welcome to Good Homes – your ultimate destination for all your real estate needs. Our platform showcases a wide range of properties, from luxurious estates to cozy apartments, commercial spaces to serene plots of land. We're committed to transparency, convenience, and innovation. Our comprehensive listings include detailed descriptions, high-quality images, and valuable neighborhood insights.</p>

                    <p class="lead mb-4">More than just a listing site, we're a community that shares a passion for real estate. Our blog offers expert advice and market trends to guide you through property transactions. Join us at Good Homes and let's find your perfect place in this world – because everyone deserves a Good Home.</p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center mb-5">
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">Contact Us</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </main>

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-geWF76RCwLtnZ8qwWowPQNguL3RmwHVBC9FhGdlKrxdiJJigb/j/68SIy3Te4Bkz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>
